OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FIt is possible Noah Donohoe "had lost
OL,7,Ftouch with reality and was in a
OL,8,Fpsychotic state" as he travelled
OL,9,Fthrough Belfast on the night of his
OL,10,Fdisappearance, a psychologist's
OL,11,Fstatement that was read at the inquest
OL,12,Finto his death has said.
OL,14,FHowever, jurors at Belfast Coroner's
OL,15,FCourt also heard a statement from
OL,16,Fanother expert who concluded "there is
OL,17,Fno psychiatric explanation for Noah
OL,18,FDonohoe's disappearance or death".
OL,26,@nD@]OUpD@PO]xD@^OUzD@aO]
