OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FThe 14-year-old had been planning to
OL,7,Fmeet with school friends at Cavehill
OL,8,Fafter setting out on his bike on
OL,9,FSunday June 21, 2020.
OL,11,FHe was captured on CCTV cycling
OL,12,Fthrough the city centre and then
OL,13,Ftowards the north of the city.
OL,15,FIn the final clip, the last footage of
OL,16,FNoah before he disappeared, he is seen
OL,17,Friding the bike naked.
OL,19,FHis naked body was found in an
OL,20,Funderground water tunnel on June 27,
OL,21,Fsix days after he left home.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
