OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1781104294
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FA post-mortem examination found the
OL,7,Flikely cause of death was drowning.
OL,9,FOn Monday, the court heard a statement
OL,10,Ffrom Dr Louise Bowers, forensic
OL,11,Fpsychologist, dated October 2021.
OL,13,FAmong the items Noah had in his
OL,14,Fpossession when he left home in June
OL,15,F2020 was the self-help book 12 Rules
OL,16,Ffor Life, by the author Jordan
OL,17,FPeterson.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
