OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FHe also "did not have a history of
OL,7,Fmental health difficulties" and no
OL,8,Fevidence he was experiencing any
OL,9,Fmental disorders, with "no history of
OL,10,Fself-harming behaviour or suicidal
OL,11,Fideation".
OL,13,FDr Bowers said it is possible Noah had
OL,14,Fsome "traits of autism spectrum
OL,15,Fdisorder (ASD)" but concluded he was a
OL,16,F"quirky young man with some
OL,17,Fobsessional traits" that would not
OL,18,Fhave met the threshold for diagnosis.
