OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1781104294
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FShe described Noah as a "reasonably
OL,7,Fwell-adjusted 14-year-old" but his
OL,8,Fmother had reported in the days before
OL,9,Fhis death he had become "weepy, his
OL,10,Fmood was low, had become more
OL,11,Faffectionate physically and verbally
OL,12,Ftowards her".
OL,14,FHe had become "extremely
OL,15,Fintrospective" and "rejected offers"
OL,16,Ffrom his friends to talk, being "awake
OL,17,Fin the middle of the night and
OL,18,Fsearching for things that at times had
OL,19,Fdark themes".
