OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1781104294
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FThe psychologist also ruled that Noah
OL,7,Fwas "showing signs of psychological
OL,8,Fdisturbance before he left his house"
OL,9,Fwhich became "much more concerning" on
OL,10,Fdeparture, and then showed
OL,11,F"increasingly disturbed behaviour as
OL,12,Fhe cycled through the city of Belfast".
OL,14,FHe went on to discard his rucksack and
OL,15,Flaptop, before the rest of his
OL,16,Fclothing, in what Dr Bowers described
OL,17,Fas a "sequence of unusual and
OL,18,Fperplexing behaviour".
