OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FShe ruled that a post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination of Noah's body made it
OL,8,Funlikely to be caused by taking drugs
OL,9,For alcohol or a head injury.
OL,11,FShe said symptoms of a psychotic
OL,12,Fepisode include hallucinations,
OL,13,Fdelusions and confused and disturbed
OL,14,Fthought.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
