PN,44910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1781104294
OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FWhile 14 "would be very young to be
OL,7,Fhaving a first psychotic episode" and
OL,8,Fit is practically "unheard of" for a
OL,9,Fpsychotic episode to instigate so
OL,10,Fquickly and be so dramatic, the
OL,11,Fpsychologist said there was "something
OL,12,Fritualistic" about how Noah discarded
OL,13,Fhis possessions and that "religious
OL,14,Fand philosophical themes" can be
OL,15,Fpresent in delusions.
OL,17,F"It is possible Noah had lost touch
OL,18,Fwith reality and was in a psychotic
OL,19,Fstate leading him to believe he was
OL,20,Fbeing instructed to behave in these
OL,21,Funusual ways," her statement read.
