OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FThe inquest then heard two statements
OL,7,Ffrom Dr Seena Fazel, a consultant
OL,8,Fpsychiatrist.
OL,10,FIn his first statement in November
OL,11,F2021, Dr Fazel ruled that Noah's death
OL,12,Fwas "likely suicide", but in a
OL,13,Fstatement from March 2026, given after
OL,14,Fhe had seen further material, the
OL,15,Fdoctor concluded "there is no
OL,16,Fpsychiatrist explanation for Noah
OL,17,FDonohoe's disappearance or death".
OL,26,@tD@EOUtD@TO]wD@ROUyD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
