OL,3,CNoah Donohoe may have 'lost touch with
OL,4,Creality' prior to death, court hears
OL,6,FHe said Noah's "changes to mental
OL,7,Fstate were probably not consistent
OL,8,Fwith an acute episode of low mood",
OL,9,Fadding: "I do not think there were any
OL,10,Fmental health conditions prior to his
OL,11,Fdisappearance."
